{"tid":597720,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）認真post 點解鏡片透明 但有倒影","createTime":"2018-03-19T01:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T02:22:47.000Z","uid":124008,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc755c2040965933efa64c88dc4f55af0143118","tid":597720,"uid":124008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/095053_98422a10e96846f9857f2f0764ff6fd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F095053_98422a10e96846f9857f2f0764ff6fd0.png&h=748796ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5727ef8f821cbd63c809c5f1f2bf59d439e95502","tid":597720,"uid":96308,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:53:24.000Z","msg":"曹操，因為曹永廉"},{"pid":"8cbfa4e101da21121b930339e23aba624f3dfc83","tid":597720,"uid":130897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"因為唔係完全誇明<br />\n<br />\n利申 2017dse phy 2"},{"pid":"41eeac257deb565a3cc44609465c62979161e974","tid":597720,"uid":130897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cbfa4e101da21121b930339e23aba624f3dfc83","tid":597720,"uid":130897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"因為唔係完全誇明<br />\n<br />\n利申 2017dse phy 2"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"透"},{"pid":"399d2846ce7206dfa67d33845457a35477c76131","tid":597720,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:57:26.000Z","msg":"因為有全反內射 (<em>Total Internal Ejaculation</em>) 射咗落你隻眼入面<br />\n<br />\n利申：ICT 5*"},{"pid":"e3ad3b65a47914357ab138fe636612a78b05916b","tid":597720,"uid":38623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"張圖我睇唔到倒影喎 影就有個"},{"pid":"f151ed5c0ff779e71173f98946f2ed37a73e5016","tid":597720,"uid":177288,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"google下好難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鏡片將光進行折射。折射就是把一部分本來應該往這裡射的光線折到別的地方去。那麼本來這裡應該是均勻分佈的光的，結果一折射，本來一些地方的光跑別處了，不均勻了，就是有的地方光多，有的地方光少。那這個就叫明暗區別吧，那這就叫影子吧。<br />\n<br />\n對於近視鏡片而言，它是凹透鏡，把光往四周發散，那麼中心光變少，四周光變多，影子就呈鏡片形狀。對於凸透鏡，光往中心會聚，那麼就周圍光變少，周圍就會形成環狀影子。<br />\n<br />\n利申：CE physics B"}]}